---
const ARROW_R = `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>`;
---

<section class="pb-[80px] max-w-[1290px] mx-auto px-3" id="cta-final">
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-600 to-[#7a28b8] rounded-[27px] px-[72px] py-[70px] relative overflow-hidden text-center">
    <!-- Décors -->
    <div class="absolute -left-[120px] -bottom-[120px] w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"
         style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,198,255,0.22), transparent 60%);">
    </div>
    <div class="absolute -right-[80px] -top-[80px] w-[320px] h-[320px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"
         style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent 60%);">
    </div>

    <!-- Contenu -->
    <div class="reveal relative max-w-[860px] mx-auto">
      <span class="kicker" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); color: rgba(232,198,255,0.95); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
        <span class="bar" style="background: #e8c6ff;"></span> On commence ?
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-bold text-[clamp(28px,3.2vw,44px)] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-white mb-4 text-balance" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;">
        Vous traversez quelque chose avec votre ado…<br />et vous cherchez à y voir plus clair&nbsp;?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/75 text-[16px] leading-[1.6] mb-2">
        Même si c'est encore flou.
      </p>
      <p class="text-white/65 text-[15px] leading-[1.65] mb-10 max-w-[540px] mx-auto">
        Parfois, il ne s'agit pas encore d'agir. Mais simplement de pouvoir dire&nbsp;:<br />
        <em class="not-italic font-semibold text-white/85">«&nbsp;voilà ce que je vis… et je ne comprends pas&nbsp;»</em><br />
        Et voir… ce qui devient plus clair.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3.5">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-8 py-[15px] bg-white text-violet-600 rounded-[999px] font-bold text-[16px] shadow-[0_8px_28px_rgba(0,0,0,0.18)] hover:bg-violet-50 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[0_14px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.22)] transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer no-underline"
          style="font-family: 'Epilogue', sans-serif;"
        >
          Recevoir un premier éclairage
          <Fragment set:html={ARROW_R} />
        </a>
        <a
          href="/#faq"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-[26px] py-[13px] bg-transparent text-white border-2 border-white/40 rounded-[999px] font-bold text-[16px] hover:border-white/80 hover:bg-white/8 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer no-underline"
          style="font-family: 'Epilogue', sans-serif;"
        >
          Lire les questions fréquentes
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Avatar + citation -->
      <div class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <div class="relative flex-shrink-0" style="width: 54px; height: 54px;">
          <!-- Anneau dégradé tournant -->
          <div class="absolute rounded-full animate-spin-border"
               style="inset: -3px; background: conic-gradient(from 0deg, #9e6bc0, #e8c6ff, #ff9477, #ffd4c8, #e8c6ff, #9e6bc0);">
          </div>
          <!-- Photo -->
          <div class="absolute rounded-full bg-center bg-cover"
               style="inset: 3px; background-image: url('/images/Claire%20J-25.avif');">
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-[13.5px] italic text-left">
          Appel de 15 min offert — sans engagement.<br />
          <span class="not-italic font-medium text-white/75">Claire, psychologue à Blagnac &amp; en visio</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
